latestPosts.caption:
Happy birthday sam 💗🫂
Your the one who never fails to make me laugh and matches my craziness and makes it 10 times more crazier....🥂
You are younger than me but you always understood me, made me understand,and tolerated my anger. You know that everyone only needs 2 true friends at most, and in a very short time, you became one of those two...🧿🤌
Once again many many happy returns of the day baby🩷🫶

सपने होते सच,तब मजा आता सोने मे✨ 

What an unforgettable journey this has been—blessed to have shared it with the most amazing people. I’m truly grateful to every single soul who stood by me; none of this would’ve been possible without you.
We dreamed together, we worked hard, and we made it happen.

As I’ve always said, rap has been my biggest support through every phase of life. That’s why I’ve always believed:
“I’ll rap till I die.” 🙇🏻‍♂️

With that, the shoot for Unwritten Verses is officially complete.
All love and gratitude to the art that saved me—Rap. ❤️🎤
